= Background

The project combines #gls("aria-synthetic-environments") scene assets, #gls("egocentric-foundation-model-3d") features, oracle #gls("relative-reconstruction-improvement") labels, and VIN-style candidate scoring. Shared notation and glossary definitions are imported from the ARIA-NBV Typst shared modules, so thesis chapters can use symbols such as $#symb.oracle.rri$ and equations such as #eqs.rri.rri.
